data.title: 6996 M 26, Eagle Harbor, MI 49950
data.meta_description: 6996 M 26, Eagle Harbor, MI 49950 is pending. Zillow has 48 photos of this 2 beds, 2 baths, 1,823 Square Feet single family home with a list price of $599,000.
data.text: Great Sand Bay is located in Upper Peninsula's Keweenaw County. It is one of the greatest beaches on Lake Superior! The stunning sunsets off to the west over the lake and mountain like views off to the east are truly amazing. The cabin was placed perfectly in this setting to give you the best of both. The cabin has an amazing kitchen! Great spot for winter sports enthusiasts. Snowmobile trail is 3 miles. Cross country ski trails less than a mile away and 20 minutes away from Mount Bohemia. The living room features vaulted ceilings and a beautiful custom-built stone fireplace. The dining area is a focal point of the home, open to the kitchen, featuring a Bosch dishwasher, a commercial size Viking gas range, a side by side refrigerator along with custom cabinets and countertops. Property has a Generac backup generator. Property is currently being used as a successful vacation rental with good occupancy in summer, fall and winter. Seller is a licensed State of Michigan Real Estate Broker. 2024-08-12
